{"type":"message","id":"aae3fb93","parentId":"8f3236cd","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:36:11.165Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's no existing template for \"欠税企业调查情况表\" in the workspace. The replied message mentioned a template structure, but I don't have the actual template file. Let me check the data more carefully - specifically looking at enterprises with actual tax arrears (欠税余额 > 0) - and then create the output Excel files organized by district.\n\nLet me first read all the data to understand what's available.","thinkingSignature":"574f8ac3d83005d9b74d56fd17aaf17f6318ad689ef7e61154283c21816532e0"},{"type":"text","text":"没有找到现成模板，我需要先了解完整数据结构，然后为你生成分区欠税表。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n8luxk8npaiy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && python3 -c \"\nimport openpyxl\nwb = openpyxl.load_workbook('/Users/ling/.openclaw/media/inbound/æ_ç_ä¼_ä_è_æ_æ_å_µè_impala---09ee70a4-cce4-4f7c-95b8-eb6e20cd77a9.xlsx')\nws = wb['Sheet 1']\n\nheaders = [c.value for c in ws[1]]\nprint('列名:', headers)\n\n# 读取所有数据\nrows = []\nfor row in ws.iter_rows(min_row=2, values_only=True):\n    rows.append(dict(zip(headers, row)))\n\n# 筛选有欠税余额的企业\nwith_arrears = [r for r in rows if r.get('当前欠税余额') and r.get('当前欠税余额') > 0]\nprint(f'\\\\n总企业数: {len(rows)}')\nprint(f'有欠税余额的企业数: {len(with_arrears)}')\n\n# 按区县局分组\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nby_district = defaultdict(list)\nfor r in rows:\n    district_raw = r.get('区县局', '') or ''\n    # 归一化区县名\n    d = district_raw\n    if '自流井' in d:\n        key = '自流井'\n    elif '贡井' in d:\n        key = '贡井'\n    elif '大安' in d:\n        key = '大安'\n    elif '沿滩' in d:\n        key = '沿滩'\n    elif '荣县' in d:\n        key = '荣县'\n    elif '富顺' in d:\n        key = '富顺'\n    elif '高新' in d or '高新' in d:\n        key = '高新'\n    else:\n        key = '其他'\n        print(f'  未识别区县: {d}')\n    by_district[key].append(r)\n\nprint('\\\\n各区县企业数:')\nfor k, v in sorted(by_district.items()):\n    with_ar = [r for r in v if r.get('当前欠税余额') and r.get('当前欠税余额') > 0]\n    print(f'  {k}: 共{len(v)}家，有欠税{len(with_ar)}家')\n\nprint('\\\\n有欠税余额的企业明细:')\nfor r in with_arrears:\n    print(f'  {r.get(\\\"纳税人名称\\\")} | 欠税={r.get(\\\"当前欠税余额\\\")} | 状态={r.get(\\\"纳税人状态\\\")} | 行业={r.get(\\\"实际行业\\\")}')\n\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5697,"output":699,"cacheRead":38499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44895,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774233352752}}
