{"type":"message","id":"7ace57c8","parentId":"842a9c04","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:37:25.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All files are generated. Now let me upload them to Feishu. Actually, let me first upload them to Feishu as files.\n\nActually, looking at the data - 12 enterprises in 大安 have tax arrears data. Let me verify by looking at what we have.\n\nWait - the data shows \"有欠税余额\" = 90 out of 102. But all 102 were included in the output (sorted by tax arrears, some have 0). Let me check if the user wants only those with arrears or all. The \"欠税企业调查情况表\" typically includes all enterprises in the district, with tax arrears highlighted. So including all 102 is correct.\n\n\nI've generated the 7 district files as requested, and now I'm verifying the totals match the expected distribution across all districts - 自流井, 贡井, 大安, 沿滩, 荣县, 富顺, and 高新 all check out to 102 enterprises total.\n\nThe files are formatted with proper styling, district-specific sheets, color coding for different status types, and frozen headers for easy navigation. Now I'm sending these to the user on Feishu.","thinkingSignature":"62986b26c8315765e23969f3e82738ece0b0423601083d9d7f1f117f1a278ef4"},{"type":"text","text":"7个区县文件全部生成完毕，正在推送到飞书：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5yuazrdux2vd_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"**✅ 分户欠税企业调查情况表已生成完毕**\n\n📁 输出路径：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/输出_欠税企业调查情况表/`\n\n共生成 **7个区县文件**，合计 **102家企业**：\n\n| 区县 | 企业数 |\n|------|--------|\n| 荣县 | 22家 |\n| 自流井 | 17家 |\n| 富顺 | 16家 |\n| 高新 | 16家 |\n| 大安 | 12家 |\n| 沿滩 | 11家 |\n| 贡井 | 8家 |\n\n**表格说明：**\n- 每张表按欠税余额降序排列\n- 橙色底=有欠税余额，红色底=欠税500万以上\n- 粉色底=非正常户\n- 底部黄色合计行含汇总金额\n- 第3行起为数据，第1行冻结\n\n文件清单：\n```\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/自流井/自流井_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/贡井/贡井_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/大安/大安_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/沿滩/沿滩_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/荣县/荣县_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/富顺/富顺_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n输出_欠税企业调查情况表/高新/高新_欠税企业调查情况表.xlsx\n```"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12481,"output":653,"cacheRead":38499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51633,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774233428006}}
