{"type":"message","id":"438e321a","parentId":"6705b152","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:41:11.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is replying to a message that describes what they want - they want a Python script that takes Impala data (one row per taxpayer) and generates per-taxpayer individual \"欠税企业调查情况表\" files, organized by district (7 districts). \n\nBut they said \"你理解错了，我不是要这样的表，我是需要这样的表\" - meaning the tables I generated are not what they need. They want the actual欠税企业调查情况表 format, which is a specific official form template.\n\nThe problem is I don't have the actual template file. The user is saying my output isn't correct. Let me re-read the replied message carefully.\n\nThe replied message says: \"我需要你写一段python代码，能够将一张表里有上百个纳税人数据（每一个纳税人的数据为一行），生成每一个纳税人一张这个欠税企业调查情况表\"\n\n\nSo they want a Python script (not the tables themselves) that generates one Excel file per taxpayer, organized into folders by district. They mentioned having a specific template for the \"欠税企业调查情况表\" but didn't actually attach it. I need to clarify what the template looks like or what specific format they need, since my generated tables clearly don't match what they're expecting. they want per-taxpayer Excel files, not aggregate tables by district. I should write a Python script that generates individual Excel files organized by district folder, one per taxpayer in the dataset.","thinkingSignature":"02d0d8fd19b890bcf58521d6b28c115aa3765007e39a3775f505e8660a33ca57"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！你要的是**每个纳税人一张独立的 Excel 表**，不是按区县汇总的大表。我来写生成脚本并直接执行出结果：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mwieg9b3jgu8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport openpyxl\nfrom openpyxl.styles import Font, PatternFill, Alignment, Border, Side\nfrom openpyxl.utils import get_column_letter\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nimport os\n\nINPUT = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/media/inbound/æ_ç_ä¼_ä_è_æ_æ_å_µè_impala---09ee70a4-cce4-4f7c-95b8-eb6e20cd77a9.xlsx'\nOUTPUT_ROOT = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/输出_欠税企业调查情况表'\nos.makedirs(OUTPUT_ROOT, exist_ok=True)\n\nwb_in = openpyxl.load_workbook(INPUT)\nws_in = wb_in['Sheet 1']\nheaders = [c.value for c in ws_in[1]]\nrows = []\nfor row in ws_in.iter_rows(min_row=2, values_only=True):\n    rows.append(dict(zip(headers, row)))\n\ndef normalize_district(d):\n    d = d or ''\n    for k in ['自流井','贡井','大安','沿滩','荣县','富顺','高新']:\n        if k in d:\n            return k\n    return '其他'\n\nby_district = defaultdict(list)\nfor r in rows:\n    key = normalize_district(r.get('区县局',''))\n    by_district[key].append(r)\n\n# 样式\nHEADER_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"1F4E79\")\nHEADER_FONT = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=10)\nSECTION_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"2E75B6\")\nSECTION_FONT = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=10)\nLABEL_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"D6E4F0\")\nLABEL_FONT = Font(bold=True, size=10)\nVALUE_FONT = Font(size=10)\nCENTER = Alignment(horizontal='center', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nLEFT = Alignment(horizontal='left', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nRIGHT = Alignment(horizontal='right', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nABNORMAL_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFC7CE\")\nARREARS_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FCE4D6\")\nHIGH_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FF0000\")\nYELLOW_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFD966\")\n\nthin = Side(style='thin')\nTHIN_BORDER = Border(left=thin, right=thin, top=thin, bottom=thin)\nmed = Side(style='medium')\nMED_BORDER = Border(left=med, right=med, top=med, bottom=med)\n\ndef set_cell(ws, row, col, value, font=None, fill=None, align=None, border=None, num_format=None):\n    cell = ws.cell(row=row, column=col, value=value)\n    if font: cell.font = font\n    if fill: cell.fill = fill\n    if align: cell.alignment = align\n    if border: cell.border = border\n    if num_format: cell.number_format = num_format\n    return cell\n\ndef make_taxpayer_sheet(ws, data, seq):\n    \"\"\"生成单个纳税人的欠税企业调查情况表\"\"\"\n    ws.sheet_view.showGridLines = False\n    \n    # 列宽\n    ws.column_dimensions['A'].width = 22\n    ws.column_dimensions['B'].width = 32\n    ws.column_dimensions['C'].width = 22\n    ws.column_dimensions['D'].width = 32\n    \n    # ===== 标题 =====\n    ws.merge_cells('A1:D1')\n    c = ws['A1']\n    c.value = '欠税企业调查情况表'\n    c.fill = HEADER_FILL\n    c.font = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=14)\n    c.alignment = CENTER\n    ws.row_dimensions[1].height = 32\n    # 加粗边框\n    for col in range(1,5):\n        ws.cell(row=1,column=col).border = MED_BORDER\n    \n    # ===== 基本信息区 =====\n    fields = [\n        ('纳税人名称', data.get('纳税人名称','')),\n        ('纳税人识别号', data.get('纳税人识别号','')),\n        ('主管税务机关', data.get('主管税务机关','')),\n        ('税管员', data.get('税管员','') or '（未登记）'),\n        ('纳税人状态', data.get('纳税人状态','')),\n        ('实际行业', data.get('实际行业','')),\n        ('纳税信用等级', data.get('纳税信用等级','') or '（无）'),\n    ]\n    \n    r = 2\n    for label, value in fields:\n        ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:B{r}')\n        ws.merge_cells(f'C{r}:D{r}')\n        lc = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value=label)\n        lc.fill = LABEL_FILL\n        lc.font = LABEL_FONT\n        lc.alignment = LEFT\n        lc.border = THIN_BORDER\n        vc = ws.cell(row=r, column=3, value=value)\n        is_abnormal = (label == '纳税人状态' and value == '非正常')\n        vc.fill = ABNORMAL_FILL if is_abnormal else PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFFFFF\")\n        vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n        vc.alignment = LEFT\n        vc.border = THIN_BORDER\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n        r += 1\n    \n    # ===== 财务数据区 =====\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:B{r}')\n    sc = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value='财务数据')\n    sc.fill = SECTION_FILL\n    sc.font = SECTION_FONT\n    sc.alignment = CENTER\n    sc.border = THIN_BORDER\n    ws.cell(row=r, column=3).border = THIN_BORDER\n    ws.cell(row=r, column=4).border = THIN_BORDER\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 24\n    r += 1\n    \n    finance_fields = [\n        ('发票授信额度（元）', data.get('发票授信额度')),\n        ('增值税申报金额（元）', data.get('增值税申报金额')),\n        ('发票开具金额（元）', data.get('发票开具金额')),\n        ('当前货币资金余额（元）', data.get('当前货币资金余额')),\n        ('当前欠税余额（元）', data.get('当前欠税余额')),\n    ]\n    \n    for label, value in finance_fields:\n        ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:B{r}')\n        ws.merge_cells(f'C{r}:D{r}')\n        lc = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value=label)\n        lc.fill = LABEL_FILL\n        lc.font = LABEL_FONT\n        lc.alignment = LEFT\n        lc.border = THIN_BORDER\n        \n        arrears_fill = (label.startswith('当前欠税') and value and float(value) > 0)\n        high_arrears = (label.startswith('当前欠税') and value and float(value) > 5000000)\n        vc = ws.cell(row=r, column=3)\n        if high_arrears:\n            vc.fill = HIGH_FILL\n            vc.font = Font(size=10, bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\")\n        elif arrears_fill:\n            vc.fill = ARREARS_FILL\n            vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n        else:\n            vc.fill = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFFFFF\")\n            vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n        \n        if value is not None:\n            vc.value = round(float(value), 2)\n            vc.number_format = '#,##0.00'\n        else:\n            vc.value = '（无数据）'\n            vc.font = Font(size=10, italic=True, color=\"999999\")\n        \n        vc.alignment = RIGHT\n        vc.border = THIN_BORDER\n        ws.cell(row=r, column=4).border = THIN_BORDER\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n        r += 1\n    \n    # ===== 签字盖章区 =====\n    r += 1\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:D{r}')\n    fc = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value='（本表由系统自动生成）')\n    fc.font = Font(size=9, italic=True, color=\"999999\")\n    fc.alignment = CENTER\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 18\n    \n    # 合计欠税\n    total_arrears = data.get('当前欠税余额') or 0\n    return total_arrears\n\ntotal_files = 0\ndistrict_stats = {}\n\nfor district, records in sorted(by_district.items()):\n    dir_path = os.path.join(OUTPUT_ROOT, district)\n    os.makedirs(dir_path, exist_ok=True)\n    files_created = 0\n    \n    for rec in records:\n        name = rec.get('纳税人名称', '未知企业')\n        # 清理文件名\n        safe_name = name.replace('/', '_').replace('\\\\', '_').replace('*','_').replace('?','_').replace('\"','_').replace('<','_').replace('>','_').replace('|','_').replace(':','')\n        \n        wb = openpyxl.Workbook()\n        ws = wb.active\n        arrears = make_taxpayer_sheet(ws, rec, total_files + 1)\n        \n        fname = f'{safe_name}.xlsx'\n        out_path = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        # 防重名\n        if os.path.exists(out_path):\n            fname = f'{safe_name}_{total_files+1}.xlsx'\n            out_path = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        \n        wb.save(out_path)\n        files_created += 1\n        total_files += 1\n    \n    district_stats[district] = files_created\n    print(f'  {district}: {files_created}个文件')\n\nprint(f'\\n完成！共生成 {total_files} 个纳税人独立Excel文件')\nprint(f'输出目录: {OUTPUT_ROOT}')\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":2509,"cacheRead":41315,"cacheWrite":11421,"totalTokens":55365,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774233614198}}
