{"type":"message","id":"8fe918ac","parentId":"4a188ba3","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:45:16.908Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the template structure. This is a comprehensive \"欠税企业调查情况表\" (Arrears Enterprise Investigation Form) with the following sections:\n\n1. **企业基本情况** (Enterprise Basic Info) - rows 4-18\n   - 序号1: 纳税人识别号\n   - 序号2: 纳税人名称\n   - 序号3: 市（州）局\n   - 序号4: 区县局\n   - 序号5: 主管税务机关\n   - 序号6: 税管员\n   - 序号7: 纳税人状态\n   - 序号8: 实际行业\n   - 序号9: 发票授信额度\n   - 序号10: 纳税信用等级\n   - 序号11: 增值税申报金额\n   - 序号12: 发票开具金额\n   - 序号13: 当前货币资金余额\n   - 序号14: 当前欠税余额\n   - 序号15: 在营情况\n\n2. **税款追征入库** (Tax Collection) - rows 20-22\n   - 序号16: 入库时间、入库金额、措施\n   - 序号22: 合计\n\n3. **关联企业情况** (Related Enterprises) - rows 24-26\n   - 序号17: 关联企业信息\n\n4. **资金和资产情况** (Capital and Assets) - rows 28-34\n   - 序号18: 银行存款账户\n   - 序号19: 资产情况（不动产/动产）\n\n5. **清欠计划** (Arrears Clearance Plan) - rows 36-37\n   - 序号20: 清欠计划\n\n6. **执法手段运用** (Enforcement Measures) - rows 39-53\n   - 基础管理事项 (rows 40-46)\n   - 强制执行事项 (rows 47-53)\n\n7. **其他特殊事项** (Other Special Matters) - rows 55-57\n   - 序号34: 破产\n   - 序号35: 申请债权金额\n   - 序号36: 未受偿金额\n\n8. **核实人** (Verifiers) - rows 58-59\n\nThe form has 8 columns spanning A through H, with the 项目 content in column B (index 1) and 填列内容 in column D (index 3). Now I need to regenerate all 102 taxpayer files using this template structure.","thinkingSignature":"a54e6f4dc10952b3f22c62eb0235a55a453ce3eb4b5faa9991dae374e5611ace"},{"type":"text","text":"模板结构清晰了！这是一张非常详细的欠税企业调查情况表，共8列，分多个区块：\n\n**区块1 - 企业基本情况**（14项）：纳税人识别号、名称、市（州）局、区县局、税务机关、税管员、状态、行业、信用等级、授信额度、增值税申报、开票金额、货币资金、欠税余额、在营情况\n\n**区块2 - 税款追征入库**：入库时间/金额/措施（可增行）+ 合计\n\n**区块3 - 关联企业情况**（可增行）\n\n**区块4 - 资金和资产情况**：银行存款、不动产、动产\n\n**区块5 - 清欠计划**\n\n**区块6 - 执法手段运用**：基础管理（欠税公告/催缴/抵欠/阻止出境/约谈）+ 强制执行（查询账户/冻结/强扣/拍卖/法院申请/代位权/优先权）\n\n**区块7 - 其他特殊事项**：破产、债权、核销\n\n马上按模板格式重新生成所有102个文件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gp0ejz3t6gnb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport xlrd\nimport openpyxl\nfrom openpyxl.styles import Font, PatternFill, Alignment, Border, Side\nfrom openpyxl.utils import get_column_letter\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nimport os\n\nINPUT_DATA = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/media/inbound/æ_ç_ä¼_ä_è_æ_æ_å_µè_impala---09ee70a4-cce4-4f7c-95b8-eb6e20cd77a9.xlsx'\nOUTPUT_ROOT = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/输出_欠税企业调查情况表'\n\n# 读取源数据\nwb_in = openpyxl.load_workbook(INPUT_DATA)\nws_in = wb_in['Sheet 1']\nheaders = [c.value for c in ws_in[1]]\nrows = []\nfor row in ws_in.iter_rows(min_row=2, values_only=True):\n    rows.append(dict(zip(headers, row)))\n\ndef normalize_district(d):\n    d = d or ''\n    for k in ['自流井','贡井','大安','沿滩','荣县','富顺','高新']:\n        if k in d:\n            return k\n    return '其他'\n\n# 样式\nDARK_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"1F4E79\")\nMID_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"2E75B6\")\nLIGHT_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"D6E4F0\")\nORANGE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FCE4D6\")\nPINK = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFC7CE\")\nYELLOW = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFD966\")\nGRAY = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"F2F2F2\")\nWHITE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFFFFF\")\nRED_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FF0000\")\n\nHEADER_FONT = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=10)\nSECTION_FONT = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=11)\nLABEL_FONT = Font(bold=True, size=9)\nVALUE_FONT = Font(size=9)\nSMALL_FONT = Font(size=8, italic=True, color=\"666666\")\nCENTER = Alignment(horizontal='center', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nLEFT = Alignment(horizontal='left', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nRIGHT = Alignment(horizontal='right', vertical='center')\n\nthin = Side(style='thin')\nmed = Side(style='medium')\nTHIN = Border(left=thin, right=thin, top=thin, bottom=thin)\nMED = Border(left=med, right=med, top=med, bottom=med)\n\ndef sc(ws, row, col, value='', font=None, fill=None, align=None, border=None, num_fmt=None):\n    c = ws.cell(row=row, column=col, value=value)\n    if font: c.font = font\n    if fill: c.fill = fill\n    if align: c.alignment = align\n    if border: c.border = border\n    if num_fmt: c.number_format = num_fmt\n    return c\n\ndef make_form(ws, data):\n    \"\"\"按官方模板格式生成欠税企业调查情况表\"\"\"\n    ws.sheet_view.showGridLines = False\n    \n    # 设置列宽 A-H\n    widths = {'A':5, 'B':18, 'C':16, 'D':30, 'E':28, 'F':14, 'G':12, 'H':30}\n    for col, w in widths.items():\n        ws.column_dimensions[col].width = w\n\n    r = 1\n    # ===== 标题 =====\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value='欠税企业调查情况表')\n    c.fill = DARK_BLUE\n    c.font = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=14)\n    c.alignment = CENTER\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 30\n    for col in range(1,9):\n        ws.cell(row=r, column=col).border = MED\n    r += 1\n\n    # 单位行\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value='单位：元')\n    c.font = Font(size=9, italic=True)\n    c.alignment = Alignment(horizontal='right')\n    c.fill = GRAY\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 16\n    r += 1\n\n    # ===== 区块1: 企业基本情况 =====\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value='一、企业基本情况')\n    c.fill = DARK_BLUE\n    c.font = HEADER_FONT\n    c.alignment = LEFT\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    r += 1\n\n    # 表头\n    for col, txt in [(1,'序号'),(2,'项目'),(3,''),(4,'填列内容'),(5,''),(6,''),(7,''),(8,'备注')]:\n        c = ws.cell(row=r, column=col, value=txt)\n        c.fill = MID_BLUE\n        c.font = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=9)\n        c.alignment = CENTER\n        c.border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n    r += 1\n\n    basic_fields = [\n        (1, '纳税人识别号', data.get('纳税人识别号','')),\n        (2, '纳税人名称', data.get('纳税人名称','')),\n        (3, '市（州）局', '自贡'),\n        (4, '区县局', data.get('区县局','')),\n        (5, '主管税务机关', data.get('主管税务机关','')),\n        (6, '税管员', data.get('税管员','') or '（未登记）'),\n        (7, '纳税人状态', data.get('纳税人状态','')),\n        (8, '实际行业', data.get('实际行业','')),\n    ]\n    \n    # 第一批7项\n    for seq, field, val in basic_fields[:7]:\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value=seq).alignment = CENTER\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=1).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=1).fill = LIGHT_BLUE\n        \n        ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n        c = ws.cell(row=r,column=2,value=field)\n        c.fill = LIGHT_BLUE\n        c.font = LABEL_FONT\n        c.alignment = LEFT\n        c.border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n        \n        ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n        is_ab = (field == '纳税人状态' and val == '非正常')\n        vc = ws.cell(row=r,column=4,value=val)\n        vc.fill = PINK if is_ab else WHITE\n        vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n        vc.alignment = LEFT\n        vc.border = THIN\n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        \n        ws.cell(row=r,column=8,value='').border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n\n    # 序号8 实际行业（合并处理）\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value=8).alignment = CENTER\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=1).border = THIN\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=1).fill = LIGHT_BLUE\n    ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r,column=2,value='实际行业')\n    c.fill = LIGHT_BLUE\n    c.font = LABEL_FONT\n    c.alignment = LEFT\n    c.border = THIN\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n    ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n    vc = ws.cell(row=r,column=4,value=data.get('实际行业',''))\n    vc.fill = WHITE\n    vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n    vc.alignment = LEFT\n    vc.border = THIN\n    for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=8,value='').border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n    r += 1\n\n    # 序号9-14\n    more_fields = [\n        (9, '发票授信额度', data.get('发票授信额度'), '#,##0.00'),\n        (10,'纳税信用等级', data.get('纳税信用等级','') or '（无）', None),\n        (11,'增值税申报金额', data.get('增值税申报金额'), '#,##0.00'),\n        (12,'发票开具金额', data.get('发票开具金额'), '#,##0.00'),\n        (13,'当前货币资金余额', data.get('当前货币资金余额'), '#,##0.00'),\n        (14,'当前欠税余额', data.get('当前欠税余额'), '#,##0.00'),\n        (15,'在营情况', data.get('纳税人状态','') == '正常' and '在营' or '（需核实）', None),\n    ]\n    \n    for seq, field, val, num_fmt in more_fields:\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value=seq).alignment = CENTER\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=1).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=1).fill = LIGHT_BLUE\n        \n        ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n        c = ws.cell(row=r,column=2,value=field)\n        c.fill = LIGHT_BLUE\n        c.font = LABEL_FONT\n        c.alignment = LEFT\n        c.border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n        \n        ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n        is_arrears = (seq == 14 and val is not None and float(val) > 0)\n        is_high = (seq == 14 and val is not None and float(val) > 5000000)\n        vc = ws.cell(row=r,column=4)\n        if is_high:\n            vc.fill = RED_FILL\n            vc.font = Font(size=9, bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\")\n        elif is_arrears:\n            vc.fill = ORANGE\n            vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n        else:\n            vc.fill = WHITE\n            vc.font = VALUE_FONT\n        \n        if val is not None:\n            vc.value = round(float(val), 2)\n            vc.number_format = '#,##0.00'\n        else:\n            vc.value = '（无数据）'\n            vc.font = Font(size=9, italic=True, color=\"999999\")\n        vc.alignment = RIGHT\n        vc.border = THIN\n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=8,value='').border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n\n    r += 1  # 空行\n\n    # ===== 区块2: 税款追征入库 =====\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value='二、税款追征入库')\n    c.fill = DARK_BLUE\n    c.font = HEADER_FONT\n    c.alignment = LEFT\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    r += 1\n\n    # 表头\n    for col, txt in [(1,'序号'),(2,'入库时间'),(3,'入库金额（元）'),(4,'采取的措施'),(5,''),(6,''),(7,''),(8,'备注')]:\n        c = ws.cell(row=r,column=col,value=txt)\n        c.fill = MID_BLUE\n        c.font = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=9)\n        c.alignment = CENTER\n        c.border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n    r += 1\n\n    # 数据行（留2行空白）\n    for i in range(2):\n        for col in range(1,9):\n            ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n            ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = WHITE\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n\n    # 合计行\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value='').fill = YELLOW\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=1).border = THIN\n    ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r,column=2,value='合计')\n    c.fill = YELLOW\n    c.font = Font(bold=True, size=9)\n    c.alignment = CENTER\n    c.border = THIN\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n    ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n    total_val = data.get('当前欠税余额')\n    vc = ws.cell(row=r,column=4,value=round(float(total_val),2) if total_val else '')\n    vc.fill = YELLOW\n    vc.font = Font(bold=True, size=9)\n    vc.alignment = RIGHT\n    vc.border = THIN\n    vc.number_format = '#,##0.00'\n    for col in [5,6,7]: \n        ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = YELLOW\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=8,value='2026年以来追征入库合计').fill = YELLOW\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=8).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n    r += 2\n\n    # ===== 区块3: 关联企业情况 =====\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value='三、关联企业情况')\n    c.fill = DARK_BLUE\n    c.font = HEADER_FONT\n    c.alignment = LEFT\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    r += 1\n\n    # 表头\n    rel_headers = ['序号','纳税人