{"type":"message","id":"5e5149d8","parentId":"113c402f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:46:45.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is with the `basic_fields` variable - it's referencing the data directly, but `basic_fields` is defined inside the function and contains only 7 items while later the code tries to access `basic_fields[7]`. Actually the issue is that the code tries to do `data.get('增值税申报金额')` which returns `None` sometimes and then tries to do `float(None)` or something. Let me look more carefully.\n\nActually the error says `could not convert string to float: 'C'` which means somewhere `float('C')` is being called. The `纳税信用等级` can be 'C', and when I try `float(val)` in the more_fields loop, for `纳税信用等级`, the `val` is `'C'` and I'm not checking for `num_fmt` being None before calling `round(float(val), 2)`.\n \nNow I see the real problem - in the `more_fields` loop, I'm iterating through items like `(9, '发票授信额度', data.get('发票授信额度'), '#,##0.00')` where the fourth element is a number format string, and then trying to convert the value to float without checking if it's actually a number first. Looking at the basic_fields tuple structure, I see it contains 7 items but the code is trying to access index 7, which doesn't exist—that's the bug. The fix is to either extend the basic_fields data to include the 8th item (实际行业) or adjust the slicing to only iterate through what's actually available in the tuple. I see the real problem now - `basic_fields` only has 7 items (indices 0-6), but the code is trying to access `basic_fields[7]` which causes an IndexError. The issue is that `seq=8, field='实际行业', val=data.get('实际行业','')` doesn't actually exist in the tuple, so I need to either add it to the data structure or handle it separately in the loop.","thinkingSignature":"5708313834ede19f54e30fd7e41ef283201fd951859cc2245aad988264bfca88"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c543wvk5c9pg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport openpyxl\nfrom openpyxl.styles import Font, PatternFill, Alignment, Border, Side\nfrom openpyxl.utils import get_column_letter\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nimport os\n\nINPUT_DATA = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/media/inbound/æ_ç_ä¼_ä_è_æ_æ_å_µè_impala---09ee70a4-cce4-4f7c-95b8-eb6e20cd77a9.xlsx'\nOUTPUT_ROOT = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/输出_欠税企业调查情况表'\n\nwb_in = openpyxl.load_workbook(INPUT_DATA)\nws_in = wb_in['Sheet 1']\nheaders = [c.value for c in ws_in[1]]\nrows = []\nfor row in ws_in.iter_rows(min_row=2, values_only=True):\n    rows.append(dict(zip(headers, row)))\n\ndef normalize_district(d):\n    d = d or ''\n    for k in ['自流井','贡井','大安','沿滩','荣县','富顺','高新']:\n        if k in d:\n            return k\n    return '其他'\n\n# 样式\nDARK_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"1F4E79\")\nMID_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"2E75B6\")\nLIGHT_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"D6E4F0\")\nORANGE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FCE4D6\")\nPINK = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFC7CE\")\nYELLOW = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFD966\")\nGRAY = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"F2F2F2\")\nWHITE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFFFFF\")\nRED_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FF0000\")\n\nthin = Side(style='thin')\nmed = Side(style='medium')\nTHIN = Border(left=thin, right=thin, top=thin, bottom=thin)\nMED = Border(left=med, right=med, top=med, bottom=med)\nCENTER = Alignment(horizontal='center', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nLEFT = Alignment(horizontal='left', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nRIGHT = Alignment(horizontal='right', vertical='center')\n\ndef write_cell(ws, row, col, value='', bold=False, font_color='000000', fill=None, align=None, border=None, num_fmt=None, size=9, italic=False):\n    c = ws.cell(row=row, column=col, value=value)\n    c.font = Font(bold=bold, size=size, color=font_color, italic=italic)\n    if fill: c.fill = fill\n    if align: c.alignment = align\n    if border: c.border = border\n    if num_fmt: c.number_format = num_fmt\n    return c\n\ndef section_title(ws, r, text):\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r, column=1, value=text)\n    c.fill = DARK_BLUE\n    c.font = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=11)\n    c.alignment = LEFT\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n\ndef col_header_row(ws, r, headers_list):\n    for col, txt in enumerate(headers_list, 1):\n        c = ws.cell(row=r, column=col, value=txt)\n        c.fill = MID_BLUE\n        c.font = Font(bold=True, color=\"FFFFFF\", size=9)\n        c.alignment = CENTER\n        c.border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n\ndef blank_data_rows(ws, r, count=2):\n    for _ in range(count):\n        for col in range(1,9):\n            ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n            ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = WHITE\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n    return r\n\ndef make_form(ws, data):\n    ws.sheet_view.showGridLines = False\n    for col, w in [('A',5),('B',18),('C',16),('D',30),('E',28),('F',14),('G',12),('H',30)]:\n        ws.column_dimensions[col].width = w\n\n    r = 1\n    # 标题\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value='欠税企业调查情况表')\n    c.fill = DARK_BLUE; c.font = Font(bold=True,color=\"FFFFFF\",size=14)\n    c.alignment = CENTER\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = MED\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 30\n    r += 1\n\n    # 单位\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    c = ws.cell(row=r,column=1,value='单位：元')\n    c.font = Font(size=9,italic=True); c.alignment = Alignment(horizontal='right')\n    c.fill = GRAY; ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 16; r += 1\n\n    # --- 企业基本情况 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '一、企业基本情况'); r += 1\n    col_header_row(ws, r, ['序号','项目','','填列内容','','','','备注']); r += 1\n\n    basic = [\n        (1,'纳税人识别号', data.get('纳税人识别号','')),\n        (2,'纳税人名称', data.get('纳税人名称','')),\n        (3,'市（州）局', '自贡'),\n        (4,'区县局', data.get('区县局','')),\n        (5,'主管税务机关', data.get('主管税务机关','')),\n        (6,'税管员', data.get('税管员','') or '（未登记）'),\n        (7,'纳税人状态', data.get('纳税人状态','')),\n        (8,'实际行业', data.get('实际行业','')),\n        (9,'发票授信额度', data.get('发票授信额度')),\n        (10,'纳税信用等级', data.get('纳税信用等级','') or '（无）'),\n        (11,'增值税申报金额', data.get('增值税申报金额')),\n        (12,'发票开具金额', data.get('发票开具金额')),\n        (13,'当前货币资金余额', data.get('当前货币资金余额')),\n        (14,'当前欠税余额', data.get('当前欠税余额')),\n        (15,'在营情况', '在营' if data.get('纳税人状态','') == '正常' else '（需核实）'),\n    ]\n\n    num_fmt_cols = {9,11,12,13,14}\n\n    for seq, field, val in basic:\n        is_ab = (field == '纳税人状态' and val == '非正常')\n        is_high = (field == '当前欠税余额' and val is not None and float(val or 0) > 5000000)\n        is_arr = (field == '当前欠税余额' and val is not None and float(val or 0) > 0)\n        \n        write_cell(ws, r, 1, seq, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        \n        ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n        write_cell(ws, r, 2, field, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN, bold=True, size=9)\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n        \n        ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n        cell_fill = RED_FILL if is_high else (PINK if is_ab else (ORANGE if is_arr else WHITE))\n        cell_font_color = \"FFFFFF\" if is_high else \"000000\"\n        \n        if val is not None and val != '' and seq in num_fmt_cols:\n            disp_val = round(float(val), 2)\n            write_cell(ws, r, 4, disp_val, fill=cell_fill, align=RIGHT, border=THIN, num_fmt='#,##0.00', font_color=cell_font_color, bold=is_high)\n        else:\n            disp_val = val if (val is not None and val != '') else '（无数据）'\n            write_cell(ws, r, 4, disp_val, fill=cell_fill, align=LEFT if seq in (2,4,5,6,7,8,10,15) else RIGHT, border=THIN, font_color=cell_font_color if val else \"999999\", italic=(val is None or val == ''), bold=is_high)\n        \n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=8,value='').border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n\n    r += 1  # 空行\n\n    # --- 税款追征入库 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '二、税款追征入库'); r += 1\n    col_header_row(ws, r, ['序号','入库时间','入库金额（元）','采取的措施','','','','备注']); r += 1\n    r = blank_data_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    \n    # 合计行\n    write_cell(ws, r, 1, '', fill=YELLOW, border=THIN)\n    ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n    write_cell(ws, r, 2, '合计', fill=YELLOW, align=CENTER, border=THIN, bold=True)\n    ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n    ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n    tv = data.get('当前欠税余额')\n    write_cell(ws, r, 4, round(float(tv),2) if tv else '', fill=YELLOW, align=RIGHT, border=THIN, num_fmt='#,##0.00', bold=True)\n    for col in [5,6,7]: write_cell(ws, r, col, '', fill=YELLOW, border=THIN)\n    write_cell(ws, r, 8, '2026年以来追征入库合计', fill=YELLOW, border=THIN, size=8, italic=True)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 2\n\n    # --- 关联企业情况 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '三、关联企业情况'); r += 1\n    col_header_row(ws, r, ['序号','纳税人名称','纳税人识别号','主管税务局','关联类型','是否欠税','货币资金余额','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_data_rows(ws, r, 2); r += 1\n\n    # --- 资金和资产情况 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '四、资金和资产情况'); r += 1\n    col_header_row(ws, r, ['序号','类型','开户银行/坐落地址','面积/账号','存款/估值金额（元）','查询日期/所有权','冻结/查封情况','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_data_rows(ws, r, 2); r += 1\n    col_header_row(ws, r, ['','动产类型','名称/数量','','','','','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_data_rows(ws, r, 2); r += 1\n\n    # --- 清欠计划 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '五、清欠计划'); r += 1\n    col_header_row(ws, r, ['序号','计划时间起','计划时间止','清欠类型','当期计划清缴金额（元）','是否按计划执行','累计清欠金额（元）','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_data_rows(ws, r, 3); r += 1\n\n    # --- 执法手段运用 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '六、执法手段运用'); r += 1\n    \n    # 基础管理事项\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    write_cell(ws, r, 1, '  基础管理事项', fill=MID_BLUE, align=LEFT, font_color=\"FFFFFF\", bold=True)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    \n    mgmt = [(21,'欠税公告'),(22,'欠税催缴'),(23,'多缴抵欠'),(24,'留抵抵欠'),(25,'阻止出境'),(26,'纳税约谈')]\n    for seq, name in mgmt:\n        write_cell(ws, r, 1, seq, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n        write_cell(ws, r, 2, name, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n        ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n        ws.cell(row=r,4).border = THIN\n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,8).border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # 强制执行事项\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    write_cell(ws, r, 1, '  强制执行事项', fill=MID_BLUE, align=LEFT, font_color=\"FFFFFF\", bold=True)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    \n    enforce = [(27,'查询银行账户余额'),(28,'冻结银行存款'),(29,'强制扣缴银行存款'),(30,'拍卖、变卖'),(31,'申请法院强制执行'),(32,'行使代位权、撤销权'),(33,'行使税收优先权')]\n    for seq, name in enforce:\n        write_cell(ws, r, 1, seq, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n        write_cell(ws, r, 2, name, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n        ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n        ws.cell(row=r,4).border = THIN\n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,8).border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # --- 其他特殊事项 ---\n    section_title(ws, r, '七、其他特殊事项'); r += 1\n    special = [(34,'破产'),(35,'债权申报'),(36,'核销死欠')]\n    for seq, name in special:\n        write_cell(ws, r, 1, seq, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        ws.merge_cells(f'B{r}:C{r}')\n        write_cell(ws, r, 2, name, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN, bold=True)\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=3).border = THIN\n        ws.merge_cells(f'D{r}:G{r}')\n        ws.cell(row=r,4).border = THIN\n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,8).border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # --- 签字区 ---\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    write_cell(ws, r, 1, '    核实人：（两名税务人员）                                    市（州）复核人及联系方式：', size=9)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22; r += 1\n    ws.merge_cells(f'A{r}:H{r}')\n    write_cell(ws, r, 1, '    区县局分管领导：（签字）', size=9)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n\n# 清理并生成\nimport shutil\nif os.path.exists(OUTPUT_ROOT):\n    shutil.rmtree(OUTPUT_ROOT)\nos.makedirs(OUTPUT_ROOT)\n\nby_district = defaultdict(list)\nfor r in rows:\n    key = normalize_district(r.get('区县局',''))\n    by_district[key].append(r)\n\ntotal = 0\nfor district, records in sorted(by_district.items()):\n    dir_path = os.path.join(OUTPUT_ROOT, district)\n    os.makedirs(dir_path, exist_ok=True)\n    for rec in records:\n        name = rec.get('纳税人名称', '未知')\n        safe = ''.join(c if c.isalnum() or c in ('_','-','（','）') else '_' for c in name)\n        wb = openpyxl.Workbook()\n        ws = wb.active\n        ws.title = '调查表'\n        make_form(ws, rec)\n        fname = f'{safe}.xlsx'\n        out = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        if os.path.exists(out):\n            fname = f'{safe}_{total+1}.xlsx'\n            out = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        wb.save(out)\n        total += 1\n    print(f'  {district}: {len(records)}个文件')\n\nprint(f'\\n✅ 完成！共生成 {total} 个文件（官方模板格式）')\nprint(f'路径: {OUTPUT_ROOT}')\nPYEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62309,"output":4427,"cacheRead":38499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105235,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774233917129}}
