{"type":"message","id":"3b1ef25e","parentId":"9a163399","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:52:18.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the template structure much better! The key insight is:\n\n1. **No placeholder text** - cells without data are truly blank (not \"（无数据）\")\n2. The template has **detailed sub-headers** with explanatory text in cells like:\n   - Row 14 (seq 11): \"填写2026年以来的金额\" in the value column\n   - Row 15 (seq 12): \"填写2026年以来的金额\" \n   - Row 16 (seq 13): \"填写最近一期财务报表货币资金余额\"\n   - etc.\n3. Some rows have hints in the rightmost columns like \"允许增行\"\n\n\n4. The basic info section maps 15 numbered fields across two columns (seq+field in B, value in D-F with \"填列内容\" as header), with \"在营情况\" at seq 15\n5. The tax collection section (seq 16) has headers for payment date, amount, and measures taken, with instructions noting that amounts should include payments, debt offsets, and any new arrears clearing since 2026\n6. The collection total (seq 16) shows aggregated amount with instructions to include all payments, debt offsets, and new arrears clearing since 2026\n7. Related enterprises section (seq 17) tracks taxpayer name, ID, tax bureau, relationship type, tax status, and capital balance\n8. The assets section splits into two parts: bank deposits (seq 18) covering account details, dates, and freeze status, plus a note about allowed additions, and separately (seq 19) real estate holdings with type, location, value, ownership, and seizure information including a note about residential/commercial/parking/land classifications\n9. Current liabilities section (seq 20) is cut off but appears to track repayment plans\n\n, with some fields appearing to be blank or requiring additional details\n10. Enforcement section starts at row 21 with tax arrears announcements and continues through various enforcement measures like bank account investigations, property seizure, auction procedures, and court applications for mandatory execution\n\n, each with specific reference numbers and dates\n11. Special matters section covers bankruptcy proceedings and creditor rights applications\n12. The form concludes with signature fields for two tax officials, a city-level reviewer with contact information, and a district-level leadership sign-off\n\nI'm realizing I need to strip out all the placeholder text and hint rows - just leave the cells blank where there's no data. For the basic info section, I'll keep it simple with 15 rows of key-value pairs for the tax authority data, leaving everything else empty. The other sections follow the same principle: maintain the structure but keep cells blank rather than filling in example text.","thinkingSignature":"7a13d91d65da58d52b9c40e5dd315d95d5924c270c01d0d0002d85c1226f46cf"},{"type":"text","text":"看清楚了！关键是：没有数据就完全留空，不要\"（无数据）\"占位文字。现在重新生成：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jnmqjsz6vou8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport openpyxl\nfrom openpyxl.styles import Font, PatternFill, Alignment, Border, Side\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nimport os, shutil\n\nINPUT_DATA = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/media/inbound/æ_ç_ä¼_ä_è_æ_æ_å_µè_impala---09ee70a4-cce4-4f7c-95b8-eb6e20cd77a9.xlsx'\nOUTPUT_ROOT = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/输出_欠税企业调查情况表'\n\nwb_in = openpyxl.load_workbook(INPUT_DATA)\nws_in = wb_in['Sheet 1']\nheaders = [c.value for c in ws_in[1]]\nrows_data = []\nfor row in ws_in.iter_rows(min_row=2, values_only=True):\n    rows_data.append(dict(zip(headers, row)))\n\ndef normalize_district(d):\n    d = d or ''\n    for k in ['自流井','贡井','大安','沿滩','荣县','富顺','高新']:\n        if k in d:\n            return k\n    return '其他'\n\nDARK_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"1F4E79\")\nMID_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"2E75B6\")\nLIGHT_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"D6E4F0\")\nORANGE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FCE4D6\")\nPINK = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFC7CE\")\nYELLOW = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFD966\")\nGRAY = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"F2F2F2\")\nWHITE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFFFFF\")\nRED_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FF0000\")\n\nthin = Side(style='thin')\nmed = Side(style='medium')\nTHIN = Border(left=thin, right=thin, top=thin, bottom=thin)\nMED = Border(left=med, right=med, top=med, bottom=med)\nCENTER = Alignment(horizontal='center', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nLEFT = Alignment(horizontal='left', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nRIGHT = Alignment(horizontal='right', vertical='center')\nBOTTOM_RIGHT = Alignment(horizontal='right', vertical='bottom')\nBOTTOM_LEFT = Alignment(horizontal='left', vertical='bottom')\n\ndef wc(ws, row, col, value='', bold=False, fc='000000', fill=None, align=None, border=None, nf=None, sz=9, italic=False):\n    c = ws.cell(row=row, column=col, value=value)\n    c.font = Font(bold=bold, size=sz, color=fc, italic=italic)\n    if fill: c.fill = fill\n    if align: c.alignment = align\n    if border: c.border = border\n    if nf: c.number_format = nf\n    return c\n\ndef mw(ws, r, c1, c2, value='', **kw):\n    ws.merge_cells(start_row=r, start_column=c1, end_row=r, end_column=c2)\n    return wc(ws, r, c1, value, **kw)\n\ndef sec(ws, r, text):\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, text, bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=DARK_BLUE, align=LEFT, sz=11)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n\ndef hdr(ws, r, hs, heights=None):\n    for ci, h in enumerate(hs, 1):\n        wc(ws, r, ci, h, bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=MID_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = heights if heights else 20\n\ndef sub(ws, r, text, fc='666666', italic=True, align=LEFT, sz=8):\n    \"\"\"子说明行（如\"允许增行\"、填写说明等），字体小灰色\"\"\"\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, text, bold=False, fc=fc, italic=italic, align=align, sz=sz)\n\ndef blank_rows(ws, r, n=2):\n    for _ in range(n):\n        for col in range(1,9):\n            ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n            ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = WHITE\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n    return r\n\ndef make_form(ws, data):\n    try:\n        ws.sheet_view.showGridLines = False\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n    for col, w in [('A',6),('B',20),('C',16),('D',14),('E',28),('F',14),('G',14),('H',32)]:\n        ws.column_dimensions[col].width = w\n\n    r = 1\n    # ===== 标题 =====\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '欠税企业调查情况表', bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=DARK_BLUE, align=CENTER, sz=14)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = MED\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 30; r += 1\n\n    # ===== 单位 =====\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '单位：元', sz=9, italic=True, align=Alignment(horizontal='right'), fill=GRAY)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 16; r += 1\n\n    # ===== 一、企业基本情况 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '一、企业基本情况'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','项目','','填列内容','','','','备注']); r += 1\n\n    # 数据项：序号、项目名、字段键（None表示文本值）、数字格式\n    basic = [\n        (1, '纳税人识别号', '纳税人识别号', None),\n        (2, '纳税人名称', '纳税人名称', None),\n        (3, '市（州）局', '自贡', None),\n        (4, '区县局', '区县局', None),\n        (5, '主管税务机关', '主管税务机关', None),\n        (6, '税管员', '税管员', None),\n        (7, '纳税人状态', '纳税人状态', None),\n        (8, '实际行业', '实际行业', None),\n        (9, '发票授信额度', '发票授信额度', '#,##0.00'),\n        (10,'纳税信用等级', '纳税信用等级', None),\n        (11,'增值税申报金额', '增值税申报金额', '#,##0.00'),\n        (12,'发票开具金额', '发票开具金额', '#,##0.00'),\n        (13,'当前货币资金余额', '当前货币资金余额', '#,##0.00'),\n        (14,'当前欠税余额', '当前欠税余额', '#,##0.00'),\n        (15,'在营情况', '在营情况', None),\n    ]\n\n    for seq, field, field_key, num_fmt in basic:\n        is_ab = (field == '纳税人状态' and data.get('纳税人状态','') == '非正常')\n        \n        raw_val = data.get(field_key, '') if isinstance(field_key, str) else field_key\n        try:\n            v = float(raw_val) if raw_val not in (None,'') else None\n        except (TypeError, ValueError):\n            v = None\n\n        is_high = (field == '当前欠税余额' and v is not None and v > 5000000)\n        is_arr = (field == '当前欠税余额' and v is not None and v > 0)\n        \n        cell_fill = RED_FILL if is_high else (PINK if is_ab else (ORANGE if is_arr else WHITE))\n        cell_fc = \"FFFFFF\" if is_high else \"000000\"\n        \n        wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 2, 3, field, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN, sz=9)\n        mw(ws, r, 4, 7, '', fill=cell_fill, border=THIN)\n        \n        # 有值才填入，否则留空\n        if raw_val not in (None, ''):\n            if num_fmt:\n                wc(ws, r, 4, round(v, 2), fill=cell_fill, align=RIGHT, border=THIN, nf=num_fmt, fc=cell_fc, bold=is_high)\n            else:\n                wc(ws, r, 4, raw_val, fill=cell_fill, align=LEFT, border=THIN, fc=cell_fc, bold=is_high)\n        \n        for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        ws.cell(row=r,column=8).border = THIN\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n\n    r += 1\n\n    # ===== 二、税款追征入库 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '二、税款追征入库'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','入库时间','入库金额（元）','采取的措施','','','','备注']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    \n    sub(ws, r, '包括入库、抵欠，2026年以来新产生欠税后清欠也计入。（允许增行）', fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True); r += 1\n\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 2, '', fill=YELLOW, border=THIN)\n    mw(ws, r, 2, 3, '合计', bold=True, fill=YELLOW, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    tv = data.get('当前欠税余额')\n    try:\n        tv_val = round(float(tv), 2)\n    except (TypeError, ValueError):\n        tv_val = None\n    mw(ws, r, 4, 7, tv_val if tv_val else '', fill=YELLOW, align=RIGHT, border=THIN, nf='#,##0.00', bold=True)\n    for col in [5,6,7]: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = YELLOW; ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    wc(ws, r, 8, '', fill=YELLOW, border=THIN)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 2\n\n    # ===== 三、关联企业情况 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '三、关联企业情况'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','纳税人名称','纳税人识别号','主管税务局','关联类型','是否欠税','货币资金余额','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    sub(ws, r, '关联类型说明：法定代表人关联/股东关联。（允许增行）', fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True); r += 1\n\n    # ===== 四、资金和资产情况 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '四、资金和资产情况'); r += 1\n    # 银行存款\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','全部银行存款账户','开户银行','存款帐号','存款余额（元）','查询日期','冻结情况','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    sub(ws, r, '（允许增行）', fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True); r += 1\n    # 不动产\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','资产情况—不动产','不动产坐落地址','不动产面积','估值金额（元）','所有权','查封情况','']); r += 1\n    sub(ws, r, '类型：住宅/商业/车位/土地。（允许增行）', fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 16; r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    # 动产\n    hdr(ws, r, ['','动产持有类型','名称/数量','','','','扣押情况','']); r += 1\n    sub(ws, r, '填写车辆、证券、基金等大额动产持有情况。（允许增行）', fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 16; r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n\n    # ===== 五、清欠计划 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '五、清欠计划'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','计划时间起','计划时间止','清欠计划类型','当期计划清缴金额（元）','是否按清欠计划执行','2026年累计按计划清欠金额（元）','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 3)\n\n    # ===== 六、执法手段运用 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '六、执法手段运用'); r += 1\n    \n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '  基础管理事项', bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=MID_BLUE, align=LEFT, sz=10)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    \n    # 基础管理表头\n    hdr(ws, r, ['','','项目','开展次数','','备注','','']); r += 1\n    \n    for seq, name, note_col5 in [\n        (21,'欠税公告', '填写最近一次公告时间'),\n        (22,'欠税催缴', '填写最近一次催缴时间'),\n        (23,'多缴抵欠', '填写2026年以来的抵欠金额'),\n        (24,'留抵抵欠', '填写2026年以来的抵欠金额'),\n        (25,'阻止出境', '填写当前阻止出境起止时间'),\n        (26,'纳税约谈', '填写最近一次约谈时间'),\n    ]:\n        wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n        wc(ws, r, 2, '', fill=LIGHT_BLUE, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 2, 3, name, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 4, 5, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 6, 7, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN)\n        wc(ws, r, 8, note_col5, fill=WHITE, border=THIN, fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # 强制执行表头\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '  强制执行事项', bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=MID_BLUE, align=LEFT, sz=10)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    \n    hdr(ws, r, ['','','项目','开展时间（最近一次）','','金额（元）','','']); r += 1\n    \n    for seq, name, note in [\n        (27,'查询银行账户余额',''),\n        (28,'冻结银行存款',''),\n        (29,'强制扣缴银行存款','最近一次扣缴：    元；2026年以来累计扣缴：    元'),\n        (30,'拍卖、变卖','最近一次拍卖变卖：    元；2026年以来累计拍卖变卖：    元'),\n        (31,'申请法院强制执行','填写申请时间：           法院受理文书号：'),\n        (32,'行使代位权、撤销权','填写申请时间：           追缴金额：'),\n        (33,'行使税收优先权','填写时间：           追缴金额：'),\n    ]:\n        wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 2, 3, name, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 4, 5, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 6, 7, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN)\n        wc(ws, r, 8, note, fill=WHITE, border=THIN, fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # ===== 七、其他特殊事项 =====\n    sec(ws, r, '七、其他特殊事项'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','','','','法院受理文书号','债权/受偿/核销金额','','']); r += 1\n    \n    for seq, name, note in [\n        (34,'破产',''),\n        (35,'债权申报','清算受偿金额：'),\n        (36,'核销死欠','申请核销死欠的时间：           核销金额：'),\n    ]:\n        wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 2, 3, name, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 4, 5, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN)\n        mw(ws, r, 6, 7, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN)\n        wc(ws, r, 8, note, fill=WHITE, border=THIN, fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # ===== 签字区 =====\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 4, '    核实人：（两名税务人员）', sz=9, fill=GRAY)\n    mw(ws, r, 5, 8, '市（州）复核人及联系方式：', sz=9, fill=GRAY, align=Alignment(horizontal='right'))\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 24; r += 1\n\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '    区县局分管领导：（签字）', sz=9, fill=GRAY)\n    for col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 24\n\ndef sf(name):\n    result = []\n    for c in name:\n        if c.isalnum() or c in ('_','-','（','）',' '):\n            result.append(c)\n        else:\n            result.append('_')\n    return ''.join(result)\n\nif os.path.exists(OUTPUT_ROOT):\n    shutil.rmtree(OUTPUT_ROOT)\nos.makedirs(OUTPUT_ROOT)\n\nby_district = defaultdict(list)\nfor rec in rows_data:\n    key = normalize_district(rec.get('区县局',''))\n    by_district[key].append(rec)\n\ntotal = 0\nfor district, records in sorted(by_district.items()):\n    dir_path = os.path.join(OUTPUT_ROOT, district)\n    os.makedirs(dir_path, exist_ok=True)\n    for rec in records:\n        name = rec.get('纳税人名称', '未知')\n        fname = sf(name) + '.xlsx'\n        out = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        if os.path.exists(out):\n            fname = sf(name) + '_' + str(total+1) + '.xlsx'\n            out = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        wb = openpyxl.Workbook()\n        ws = wb.active\n        ws.title = '调查表'\n        make_form(ws, rec)\n        wb.save(out)\n        total += 1\n    print(f'  {district}: {len(records)}个文件')\n\nprint(f'\\n完成！共生成 {total} 个文件')\nPYEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80191,"output":5221,"cacheRead":38499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123911,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774234234146}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ef40ff8","parentId":"3b1ef25e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:52:18.787Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jnmqjsz6vou8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 309, in <module>\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 160, in make_form\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 54, in mw\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 44, in wc\n  File \"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/openpyxl/worksheet/worksheet.py\", line 246, in cell\n    cell.value = value\n    ^^^^^^^^^^\nAttributeError: 'MergedCell' object attribute 'value' is read-only\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":301,"aggregated":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 309, in <module>\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 160, in make_form\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 54, in mw\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 44, in wc\n  File \"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/lib/python3.14/site-packages/openpyxl/worksheet/worksheet.py\", line 246, in cell\n    cell.value = value\n    ^^^^^^^^^^\nAttributeError: 'MergedCell' object attribute 'value' is read-only\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774234338762}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d026e09","parentId":"0ef40ff8","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:53:45.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that `mw` merges cells starting from c1, and then sets the value on the top-left cell. But if the cells in the range have already been merged (or if the merged range overlaps), it fails.\n\nThe problem is at line 160:\n```python\nmw(ws, r, 2, 3, name, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN)\nwc(ws, r, 2, '', fill=LIGHT_BLUE, border=THIN)  # This tries to write to a merged cell\n```\n\nNo wait, the issue is:\n\n\n```python\nmw(ws, r, 1, 4, '    核实人：（两名税务人员）', sz=9, fill=GRAY)\nmw(ws, r, 5, 8, '市（州）复核人及联系方式：', sz=9, fill=GRAY, align=Alignment(horizontal='right'))\nfor col in range(1,9): ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN  # This tries to set border on merged cells\n```\n\nThe border loop at the end is trying to apply borders to cells that are already part of a merge, which causes the error.\n\nThe problem is that when cells are merged, I can only set properties on the top-left cell of the merged range. Setting borders on any other cell in a merged range fails. I need to either apply the border only to the top-left cell before merging, or skip the border assignment for cells within an already-merged range.","thinkingSignature":"acbd3226205512a1518edf8a350872d6a3fce372df6f561bef7a5bcf73ec6222"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0gqicfh6rzqr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport openpyxl\nfrom openpyxl.styles import Font, PatternFill, Alignment, Border, Side\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nimport os, shutil\n\nINPUT_DATA = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/media/inbound/æ_ç_ä¼_ä_è_æ_æ_å_µè_impala---09ee70a4-cce4-4f7c-95b8-eb6e20cd77a9.xlsx'\nOUTPUT_ROOT = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/输出_欠税企业调查情况表'\n\nwb_in = openpyxl.load_workbook(INPUT_DATA)\nws_in = wb_in['Sheet 1']\nheaders = [c.value for c in ws_in[1]]\nrows_data = []\nfor row in ws_in.iter_rows(min_row=2, values_only=True):\n    rows_data.append(dict(zip(headers, row)))\n\ndef normalize_district(d):\n    d = d or ''\n    for k in ['自流井','贡井','大安','沿滩','荣县','富顺','高新']:\n        if k in d: return k\n    return '其他'\n\nDARK_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"1F4E79\")\nMID_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"2E75B6\")\nLIGHT_BLUE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"D6E4F0\")\nORANGE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FCE4D6\")\nPINK = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFC7CE\")\nYELLOW = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFD966\")\nGRAY = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"F2F2F2\")\nWHITE = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FFFFFF\")\nRED_FILL = PatternFill(\"solid\", fgColor=\"FF0000\")\n\nthin = Side(style='thin')\nmed = Side(style='medium')\nTHIN = Border(left=thin, right=thin, top=thin, bottom=thin)\nMED = Border(left=med, right=med, top=med, bottom=med)\nCENTER = Alignment(horizontal='center', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nLEFT = Alignment(horizontal='left', vertical='center', wrap_text=True)\nRIGHT = Alignment(horizontal='right', vertical='center')\n\ndef wc(ws, row, col, value='', bold=False, fc='000000', fill=None, align=None, border=None, nf=None, sz=9, italic=False):\n    if col < 1 or col > 8: return\n    c = ws.cell(row=row, column=col)\n    # skip merged cells (read-only)\n    try:\n        c.value = value\n    except (AttributeError, TypeError):\n        return\n    c.font = Font(bold=bold, size=sz, color=fc, italic=italic)\n    if fill: c.fill = fill\n    if align: c.alignment = align\n    if border: c.border = border\n    if nf: c.number_format = nf\n\ndef mw(ws, r, c1, c2, value='', bold=False, fc='000000', fill=None, align=None, border=None, nf=None, sz=9, italic=False, skip_border=False):\n    ws.merge_cells(start_row=r, start_column=c1, end_row=r, end_column=c2)\n    wc(ws, r, c1, value, bold=bold, fc=fc, fill=fill, align=align, sz=sz, italic=italic)\n    if border and not skip_border:\n        for col in range(c1, c2+1):\n            try:\n                ws.cell(row=r, column=col).border = border\n            except (AttributeError, TypeError):\n                pass\n\ndef sec(ws, r, text):\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, text, bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=DARK_BLUE, align=LEFT, sz=11)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 22\n\ndef hdr(ws, r, hs, row_h=20):\n    for ci, h in enumerate(hs, 1):\n        wc(ws, r, ci, h, bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=MID_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = row_h\n\ndef note_row(ws, r, text, h=16):\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, text, fc='888888', italic=True, align=LEFT, sz=8)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = h\n\ndef blank_rows(ws, r, n=2):\n    for _ in range(n):\n        for col in range(1,9):\n            try:\n                ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n                ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = WHITE\n            except (AttributeError, TypeError):\n                pass\n        ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n        r += 1\n    return r\n\ndef data_row(ws, r, seq, field, field_key, data, num_fmt=None, note=''):\n    is_ab = (field == '纳税人状态' and data.get('纳税人状态','') == '非正常')\n    raw_val = data.get(field_key, '') if isinstance(field_key, str) else field_key\n    try:\n        v = float(raw_val) if raw_val not in (None,'') else None\n    except (TypeError, ValueError):\n        v = None\n\n    is_high = (field == '当前欠税余额' and v is not None and v > 5000000)\n    is_arr = (field == '当前欠税余额' and v is not None and v > 0)\n    cell_fill = RED_FILL if is_high else (PINK if is_ab else (ORANGE if is_arr else WHITE))\n    cell_fc = \"FFFFFF\" if is_high else \"000000\"\n\n    wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    mw(ws, r, 2, 3, field, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN, sz=9)\n    mw(ws, r, 4, 7, '', fill=cell_fill, border=THIN, skip_border=True)\n    if raw_val not in (None, ''):\n        align = RIGHT if num_fmt else LEFT\n        wc(ws, r, 4, round(v,2) if num_fmt else raw_val, fill=cell_fill, align=align, border=THIN, nf=num_fmt, fc=cell_fc, bold=is_high)\n    if note:\n        wc(ws, r, 8, note, fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n\ndef mgmt_row(ws, r, seq, name, note=''):\n    wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    mw(ws, r, 2, 3, name, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN)\n    mw(ws, r, 4, 5, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN, skip_border=True)\n    mw(ws, r, 6, 7, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN, skip_border=True)\n    wc(ws, r, 8, note, fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n\ndef special_row(ws, r, seq, name, note=''):\n    wc(ws, r, 1, seq, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    mw(ws, r, 2, 3, name, bold=True, fill=LIGHT_BLUE, align=LEFT, border=THIN)\n    mw(ws, r, 4, 5, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN, skip_border=True)\n    mw(ws, r, 6, 7, '', fill=WHITE, border=THIN, skip_border=True)\n    wc(ws, r, 8, note, fc='888888', sz=8, italic=True)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20\n\ndef make_form(ws, data):\n    try:\n        ws.sheet_view.showGridLines = False\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n    for col, w in [('A',6),('B',20),('C',16),('D',14),('E',28),('F',14),('G',14),('H',32)]:\n        ws.column_dimensions[col].width = w\n\n    r = 1\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '欠税企业调查情况表', bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=DARK_BLUE, align=CENTER, sz=14)\n    for col in range(1,9):\n        try: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = MED\n        except: pass\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 30; r += 1\n\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '单位：元', sz=9, italic=True, align=Alignment(horizontal='right'), fill=GRAY)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 16; r += 1\n\n    # --- 企业基本情况 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '一、企业基本情况'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','项目','','填列内容','','','','备注']); r += 1\n\n    for seq, field, fk, nf in [\n        (1,'纳税人识别号','纳税人识别号',None),\n        (2,'纳税人名称','纳税人名称',None),\n        (3,'市（州）局','自贡',None),\n        (4,'区县局','区县局',None),\n        (5,'主管税务机关','主管税务机关',None),\n        (6,'税管员','税管员',None),\n        (7,'纳税人状态','纳税人状态',None),\n        (8,'实际行业','实际行业',None),\n        (9,'发票授信额度','发票授信额度','#,##0.00'),\n        (10,'纳税信用等级','纳税信用等级',None),\n        (11,'增值税申报金额','增值税申报金额','#,##0.00'),\n        (12,'发票开具金额','发票开具金额','#,##0.00'),\n        (13,'当前货币资金余额','当前货币资金余额','#,##0.00'),\n        (14,'当前欠税余额','当前欠税余额','#,##0.00'),\n        (15,'在营情况','在营情况',None),\n    ]:\n        data_row(ws, r, seq, field, fk, data, num_fmt=nf)\n        r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # --- 税款追征入库 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '二、税款追征入库'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','入库时间（具体到天）','入库金额（元）','采取的措施（按计划入库、强扣、拍卖/变卖、抵欠、以债化欠等）','','','','备注']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    note_row(ws, r, '包括入库、抵欠，2026年以来新产生欠税后清欠也计入。（允许增行）'); r += 1\n\n    # 合计行\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 2, '', fill=YELLOW, border=THIN, skip_border=True)\n    mw(ws, r, 2, 3, '合计', bold=True, fill=YELLOW, align=CENTER, border=THIN)\n    tv = data.get('当前欠税余额')\n    try:\n        tv_val = round(float(tv), 2)\n    except (TypeError, ValueError):\n        tv_val = None\n    mw(ws, r, 4, 7, tv_val if tv_val else '', fill=YELLOW, align=RIGHT, border=THIN, nf='#,##0.00', bold=True, skip_border=True)\n    wc(ws, r, 4, tv_val if tv_val else '', fill=YELLOW, align=RIGHT, border=THIN, nf='#,##0.00', bold=True)\n    for col in [5,6,7]:\n        try: ws.cell(row=r,column=col).fill = YELLOW; ws.cell(row=r,column=col).border = THIN\n        except: pass\n    try: ws.cell(row=r,column=8).fill = YELLOW; ws.cell(row=r,column=8).border = THIN\n    except: pass\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 2\n\n    # --- 关联企业情况 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '三、关联企业情况'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','纳税人名称','纳税人识别号','主管税务局','关联类型','是否欠税','货币资金余额','']); r += 1\n    note_row(ws, r, '关联类型说明：法定代表人关联/股东关联。（允许增行）'); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n\n    # --- 资金和资产情况 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '四、资金和资产情况'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','全部银行存款账户','开户银行','存款帐号','存款余额（元）','查询日期','冻结情况','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n    note_row(ws, r, '（允许增行）'); r += 1\n\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','资产情况—不动产','不动产坐落地址','不动产面积','估值金额（元）','所有权','查封情况','']); r += 1\n    note_row(ws, r, '类型：住宅/商业/车位/土地。（允许增行）'); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n\n    hdr(ws, r, ['','动产持有类型','名称/数量','同类动产持有数量','估值金额（元）','所有权','扣押情况','']); r += 1\n    note_row(ws, r, '填写车辆、证券、基金等大额动产持有情况。（允许增行）'); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 2)\n\n    # --- 清欠计划 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '五、清欠计划'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','计划时间起','计划时间止','清欠计划类型（按月/按季）','当期计划清缴金额（元）','是否按清欠计划执行','2026年累计按计划清欠金额（元）','']); r += 1\n    r = blank_rows(ws, r, 3)\n\n    # --- 执法手段运用 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '六、执法手段运用'); r += 1\n    \n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '  基础管理事项', bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=MID_BLUE, align=LEFT, sz=10)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['','','项目','开展次数','','备注','','']); r += 1\n\n    for seq, name, note in [\n        (21,'欠税公告','填写最近一次公告时间'),\n        (22,'欠税催缴','填写最近一次催缴时间'),\n        (23,'多缴抵欠','填写2026年以来的抵欠金额'),\n        (24,'留抵抵欠','填写2026年以来的抵欠金额'),\n        (25,'阻止出境','填写当前阻止出境起止时间'),\n        (26,'纳税约谈','填写最近一次约谈时间'),\n    ]:\n        mgmt_row(ws, r, seq, name, note); r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '  强制执行事项', bold=True, fc='FFFFFF', fill=MID_BLUE, align=LEFT, sz=10)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 20; r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['','','项目','开展时间（最近一次）','','金额（元）','','']); r += 1\n\n    for seq, name, note in [\n        (27,'查询银行账户余额',''),\n        (28,'冻结银行存款',''),\n        (29,'强制扣缴银行存款','最近一次扣缴：    元；2026年以来累计扣缴：    元'),\n        (30,'拍卖、变卖','最近一次拍卖变卖：    元；2026年以来累计拍卖变卖：    元'),\n        (31,'申请法院强制执行','填写申请时间：           法院受理文书号：'),\n        (32,'行使代位权、撤销权','填写申请时间：           追缴金额：'),\n        (33,'行使税收优先权','填写时间：           追缴金额：'),\n    ]:\n        mgmt_row(ws, r, seq, name, note); r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # --- 其他特殊事项 ---\n    sec(ws, r, '七、其他特殊事项'); r += 1\n    hdr(ws, r, ['序号','','','法院受理时间','法院受理文书号','债权/受偿/核销金额','','']); r += 1\n\n    for seq, name, note in [\n        (34,'破产',''),\n        (35,'债权申报','清算受偿金额：'),\n        (36,'核销死欠','申请核销死欠的时间：           核销金额：'),\n    ]:\n        special_row(ws, r, seq, name, note); r += 1\n    r += 1\n\n    # --- 签字区 ---\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 4, '    核实人：（两名税务人员）', sz=9, fill=GRAY)\n    mw(ws, r, 5, 8, '市（州）复核人及联系方式：', sz=9, fill=GRAY, align=Alignment(horizontal='right'))\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 24; r += 1\n    mw(ws, r, 1, 8, '    区县局分管领导：（签字）', sz=9, fill=GRAY)\n    ws.row_dimensions[r].height = 24\n\ndef sf(name):\n    result = []\n    for c in name:\n        if c.isalnum() or c in ('_','-','（','）',' '):\n            result.append(c)\n        else:\n            result.append('_')\n    return ''.join(result)\n\nif os.path.exists(OUTPUT_ROOT):\n    shutil.rmtree(OUTPUT_ROOT)\nos.makedirs(OUTPUT_ROOT)\n\nby_district = defaultdict(list)\nfor rec in rows_data:\n    key = normalize_district(rec.get('区县局',''))\n    by_district[key].append(rec)\n\ntotal = 0\nfor district, records in sorted(by_district.items()):\n    dir_path = os.path.join(OUTPUT_ROOT, district)\n    os.makedirs(dir_path, exist_ok=True)\n    for rec in records:\n        name = rec.get('纳税人名称', '未知')\n        fname = sf(name) + '.xlsx'\n        out = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        if os.path.exists(out):\n            fname = sf(name) + '_' + str(total+1) + '.xlsx'\n            out = os.path.join(dir_path, fname)\n        wb = openpyxl.Workbook()\n        ws = wb.active\n        ws.title = '调查表'\n        make_form(ws, rec)\n        wb.save(out)\n        total += 1\n    print(f'  {district}: {len(records)}个文件')\n\nprint(f'\\n完成！共生成 {total} 个文件')\nPYEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85563,"output":4762,"cacheRead":38499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128824,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774234338788}}
