{"type":"message","id":"7ac20eb5","parentId":"959bc3fc","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:35:50.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the simulation data. Let me also check today's market situation. The report shows the simulation is up slightly (净值 1.0008, barely above 1.0). Let me also check the real market data.\n\nThe key info:\n- 模拟净值: 1.0008 (barely positive)\n- 总资产: 1,000,814 元 (gained ~814元 from 1M)\n- 持仓市值: 309,682元 (30.9% position)\n- 持仓10只，浮盈都在0.5%以内，大部分小赚\n- 市场宽度低，仓位40%\n\n\n- Report timestamp: 2026-03-23 10:59 (before market close)\n\nI should verify whether the data is from today or if it was actually from the last trading day on 20260320, since today is Monday 20260323. The report itself says \"信号日期: 2026-03-03\", which suggests this is historical data from earlier in March.\n\nLooking at the current positions, most stocks are down between 1-3% with only a couple showing modest gains, so the strategy appears to be holding up reasonably well despite the market weakness. Let me pull the actual closing prices from today to get a complete picture.","thinkingSignature":"1ed0f47e3b3c2675698619b508edc04cfdfa0efcfa37d0dfe6b182f7d5a3a8b4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_236nw31df6o0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json, subprocess\nresult = subprocess.run(['python3', '-c', '''\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\npro = ts.pro_api()\n\n# 获取主要指数今日数据\nindices = [(\"上证指数\", \"000001.SH\"), (\"创业板\", \"399006.SZ\"), (\"科创50\", \"000688.SH\")]\ntry:\n    df = pro.index_daily(ts_code=\"000001.SH\", start_date=\"20260323\", end_date=\"20260323\")\n    print(\"上证:\", df)\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(\"Error:\", e)\n'''], capture_output=True, text=True, cwd='/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system')\nprint(result.stdout[-2000:] if len(result.stdout) > 2000 else result.stdout)\nprint(result.stderr[-500:] if result.stderr else '')\nEOF