{"type":"message","id":"94eef143","parentId":"10848ddf","timestamp":"2026-03-23T09:01:35.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a market analysis for today (2026-03-23) since the market fell significantly. Let me check the current market data and also check the simulation portfolio performance. I need to check today's date and get market data.\n\nLet me check today's date first, and then try to get market data. The market should have closed by now (17:01).\n\nFor the simulation portfolio question from earlier (15:33), I never properly answered. Let me now address both - do the market analysis for today.\n\nLet me check the quant system scripts for getting today's market data.","thinkingSignature":"416bfe3850657ba46e4d95f5d8b9901900fc51ae18f8a4b05b3400d0f17aae02"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，马上分析！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ncmlf6p1momq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && /usr/bin/python3 << 'EOF'\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\npro = ts.pro_api()\n\ntoday = '20260323'\n\n# 获取主要指数今日行情\nindices = [\n    ('上证指数', '000001.SH'),\n    ('深证成指', '399001.SZ'),\n    ('创业板指', '399006.SZ'),\n    ('科创50', '000688.SH'),\n    ('沪深300', '000300.SH'),\n    ('中证500', '000905.SH'),\n    ('中证1000', '000852.SH'),\n    ('上证50', '000016.SH'),\n]\n\nprint(\"=== 今日指数行情 ===\")\nresults = []\nfor name, code in indices:\n    try:\n        df = pro.index_daily(ts_code=code, start_date=today, end_date=today)\n        if not df.empty:\n            row = df.iloc[0]\n            results.append({\n                'name': name,\n                'code': code,\n                'close': row['close'],\n                'pct_chg': row['pct_chg'],\n                'amount': row.get('amount', 0)\n            })\n            print(f\"  {name}({code}): {row['close']}  涨跌: {row['pct_chg']:+.2f}%\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"  {name}: 无数据\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  {name}: Error - {e}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n=== 全市场上涨下跌家数 ===\")\ntry:\n    # 用日线统计全市场涨跌\n    bs = pro.bsi_daily(trade_date=today)\n    if not bs.empty:\n        up = bs[bs['pct_chg'] > 0].shape[0]\n        down = bs[bs['pct_chg'] < 0].shape[0]\n        flat = bs[bs['pct_chg'] == 0].shape[0]\n        print(f\"  上涨: {up}  下跌: {down}  平盘: {flat}\")\n    else:\n        print(\"  BSI数据为空，尝试其他方式\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  BSI error: {e}\")\n\n# 涨跌停统计\ntry:\n    limit_up = pro.limit_list(trade_date=today, orient='1')\n    limit_down = pro.limit_list(trade_date=today, orient='0')\n    print(f\"  涨停: {len(limit_up)}  跌停: {len(limit_down)}\")\nexcept:\n    pass\n\n# 成交额\ntry:\n    qfq = pro.index_daily(ts_code='000001.SH', start_date=today, end_date=today, fields='ts_code,trade_date,amount')\n    if not qfq.empty:\n        amt = qfq.iloc[0]['amount']\n        print(f\"  上证成交额: {amt/1e8:.2f}亿元\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  成交额: {e}\")\n\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":824,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":149726,"totalTokens":150670,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774256468495}}
