{"type":"message","id":"9840c72a","parentId":"8a7cbdb4","timestamp":"2026-03-23T09:03:06.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me get more data on the simulation portfolio - the account balance, total P/L, etc.\n\nKey findings:\n- Market crash: All major indices fell 3-5%\n  - 上证: -3.63%\n  - 深证: -3.76%\n  - 创业板: -3.49%\n  - 科创50: -4.31%\n  - 中证1000: -4.81% (worst)\n  \n- Simulation portfolio positions:\n  - 8 out of 10 stocks fell\n  - 2 stocks rose: 禾信仪器 +15.21%, 双良节能 +4.66%\n  - Worst performers hit double digits: 英方软件 -11.38%, 明微电子 -7.80%, 掌阅科技 -6.14%\n  - The portfolio weighted average decline came in at -2.79%, which actually outperformed the broader indices\n\nLooking at the individual stock trajectories over the past week, most positions show a clear downtrend despite today's sharp selloff, with declines ranging from 3-5% across the board over the five-day period.\n\n禾信仪器 stands out as a major outperformer with explosive growth—up 36% in just three days from March 18-23, hitting the 15.21% limit today—which suggests it could be riding a specific catalyst or market narrative rather than following the broader weakness.\n\nThe market breadth is severely compressed with only 305 stocks advancing against 5,172 declining, confirming this was a broad-based liquidation event rather than selective selling. I should pull the simulation account's total holdings and overall returns to see how the strategy has held up through this drawdown.","thinkingSignature":"0918e422d7d2300d01691caa36407124b5cc370a3e392347d8a00449aaef236f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iztp551g197d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && /usr/bin/python3 << 'EOF'\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nimport json\n\npro = ts.pro_api()\ntoday = '20260323'\n\n# 读取昨日模拟账户快照\nimport os\nacct_files = sorted([f for f in os.listdir('research/reports') if 'paper_alpha55_account' in f and f.endswith('.json')], reverse=True)\nprint(\"账户文件:\", acct_files[:3])\n\npositions_files = sorted([f for f in os.listdir('research/reports') if 'alpha55_live_orders' in f and f.endswith('.csv')], reverse=True)\nprint(\"持仓文件:\", positions_files[:3])\n\n# 读取最新账户\nif acct_files:\n    with open(f'research/reports/{acct_files[0]}') as f:\n        acct = json.load(f)\n    print(f\"\\n=== 模拟账户信息 ===\")\n    print(f\"日期: {acct.get('date','')}\")\n    print(f\"总资产: {acct.get('total_assets',0):,.0f}\")\n    print(f\"可用现金: {acct.get('cash',0):,.0f}\")\n    print(f\"持仓市值: {acct.get('market_value',0):,.0f}\")\n    print(f\"净值: {acct.get('nav',0):.4f}\")\n    if 'today_pct' in acct:\n        print(f\"今日涨跌: {acct['today_pct']:+.2f}%\")\n\n# 计算模拟账户今日盈亏\npositions = [\n    ('688228.SH','开普云', 300, 104.67),\n    ('603103.SH','横店影视', 1400, 22.38),\n    ('688221.SH','前沿生物', 1700, 18.13),\n    ('688622.SH','禾信仪器', 300, 92.4),\n    ('001330.SZ','博纳影业', 4700, 6.67),\n    ('600977.SH','中国电影', 2500, 12.71),\n    ('603533.SH','掌阅科技', 1300, 24.26),\n    ('688435.SH','英方软件', 700, 43.75),\n    ('600481.SH','双良节能', 4300, 7.28),\n    ('688699.SH','明微电子', 700, 43.9),\n]\ncodes = [p[0] for p in positions]\ndf = pro.daily(ts_code=','.join(codes), trade_date=today)\ndf = df.set_index('ts_code')\n\ntotal_cost = 0\ntotal_market_val = 0\ntotal_float_pl = 0\ntotal_float_pct = 0\n\nprint(f\"\\n=== 模拟持仓明细（{today}）===\")\nfor code, name, qty, cost in positions:\n    if code in df.index:\n        close = df.loc[code, 'close']\n        pct = df.loc[code, 'pct_chg']\n        mkt_val = close * qty\n        cost_val = cost * qty\n        pl = mkt_val - cost_val\n        pl_pct = (close - cost) / cost * 100\n        total_cost += cost_val\n        total_market_val += mkt_val\n        total_float_pl += pl\n        total_float_pct += pl_pct\n        arrow = \"↑\" if pct > 0 else \"↓\" if pct < 0 else \"→\"\n        print(f\"  {arrow} {name:8s} x{qty:4d} 成本:{cost:7.2f} 现价:{close:8.2f} 今日:{pct:+6.2f}% 浮盈亏:{pl:+10.2f}({pl_pct:+.1f}%)\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  ? {name}: 无数据\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n  持仓汇总: 成本{total_cost:,.0f} 现值{total_market_val:,.0f} 浮盈亏{total_float_pl:+,.0f}({total_float_pct/len(positions):+.2f}%)\")\n\n# 计算今日组合涨跌（用持仓市值加权）\nif acct_files:\n    with open(f'research/reports/{acct_files[0]}') as f:\n        acct = json.load(f)\n    nav_yesterday = acct.get('nav', 1.0)\n    # 今日组合下跌 ≈ 组合内个股今日加权平均\n    combo_today_pct = sum(df.loc[c,'pct_chg'] * (p[2]*p[3]) for c,p in zip(codes, positions) if c in df.index) / total_cost\n    cash_ratio = acct.get('cash', 0) / acct.get('total_assets', 1)\n    actual_combo = combo_today_pct * (1 - cash_ratio) if cash_ratio < 1 else 0\n    print(f\"\\n  今日组合估算涨跌: {actual_combo:+.2f}%\")\n    print(f\"  昨日净值: {nav_yesterday:.4f}\")\n    print(f\"  今日净值估算: {nav_yesterday*(1+actual_combo/100):.4f}\")\n\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":115278,"output":1523,"cacheRead":38484,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774256547143}}
