{"type":"message","id":"4e36f8e6","parentId":"3f4b80f7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T09:24:53.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking for a free map software that can plot coordinates (latitude/longitude). Let me think about this.\n\nOptions:\n1. **QGIS** - Free, open-source, most powerful GIS software, can handle lat/long coordinates\n2. **Google Earth Pro** - Free, can plot lat/long points easily\n3. **GPS Visualizer** - Free online tool\n4. **GIMP** - Not really a map tool\n5. **Python with matplotlib/cartopy** - if they want to code it\n6. **Tableau** - has map capabilities but not free\n7. **Flourish** - can do map visualizations but not lat/long plotting\n\n\n8. **ArcGIS** - not free, but there's a free online version\n\nI should give them the most practical recommendations that actually meet their needs.","thinkingSignature":"135bbbb459361078bdf8be9dd156c8a70827f2102e2dfd4696070e1f76fe1dcd"},{"type":"text","text":"**有几个免费好用的推荐：**\n\n| 软件 | 平台 | 推荐理由 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **QGIS** | Mac/Win/Linux | 最强大的免费GIS，支持经纬度打点、导入CSV/Excel、地图底图丰富 |\n| **Google Earth Pro** | Mac/Win | 最简单，粘贴经纬度直接显示，3D地球可视化直观 |\n| **GPS Visualizer** | 在线工具 | 网址 gpsvisualizer.com，上传经纬度CSV直接出图，无需安装 |\n\n**快速上手推荐**：\n- 如果只是**偶尔画几个点** → Google Earth Pro（直接搜索栏输入\"纬度,经度\"即可）\n- 如果需要**做图、导出、批量处理** → GPS Visualizer（上传Excel表格即可）\n- 如果是**专业地图制图** → QGIS（功能最强，但有学习曲线）\n\n你是要做什么用途？我可以帮你选择最适合的工具。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":372,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":160036,"totalTokens":160528,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774257874496}}
